Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd you open the window again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some bugs may fly in again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering in which part of that building the old man saw the will-o'-the-wisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, if that's what you're looking for, it was in the very center of the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lonely red light floating in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are times when it's a pale blue light, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:14.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:19.10,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please ask the resident of room two, Yatsuya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and the resident of room four, Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've also seen the will-o'-the-wisps before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A floating red light and a floating blue light
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to see it when I dropped by my Senpai's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was in room six, which is right above this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when Senpai saw the will-o'-the-wisp, he got so scared he couldn't sleep and ended up moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep either, since I was so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:04:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, is this an 8mm film projector?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was just editing a film I did with my university's club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.48,0:05:09.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this sure is an amazing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many horror magazines and posters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seriously, I feel like I'm in a nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room is nothing compared to Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in room four.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room really is impressive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's full of monster and ghost dolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too early to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:35.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I turn off the lights like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The dolls...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are glowing in various colors!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because of this black light
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This light is reflected by the fluorescent paint on the dolls and produces a neon light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man from the toy shop taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you also see the will-o'-the-wisp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw it, but not in that building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only saw it in this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This window is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:11.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Below the window where we saw the person's shadow earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should hurry up and close that window.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For this girl's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, two or three have already come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, as far as people who don't believe in ghosts stories goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's the resident of room one, Botan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That thickheaded graduate student.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Correct, I've never seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:41.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I only believe in things that have been scientifically proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,However, my one complaint...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:46.75,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Would be that building next door that never finished construction, and isn't being cared for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.92,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that annoying building, most of the sunlight is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's all right for Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} above me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has a window that correctly faces the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why don't you move away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rent is cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And my grandmother told me that the feng shui of this place is great
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Didn't you say you only believe in things that have been scientifically proven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I smoke here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you have to leave after that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:29.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, on dad's arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again, a moth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why is it always me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quickly, get rid of it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The culprit was scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:01.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of being exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.49,0:08:06.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So he tried to cover it up with that ghost story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The ease that occurred four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:12.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The decisive clue that solves that burning murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night's just started...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An even scarier ghost may appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.89,0:08:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you leave, I'll finally be able to work on my thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye then, say hi to the ghosts for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, how unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making such a fuss over mere optical illusions...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, where's Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to go to the restroom first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's scary to go alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, can you go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy with the mustache...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I've seen him somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you about to head home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, this toilet, it's really cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really stinky and the water won't flush!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that it stinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the water flushes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The water turned red!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:58.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now it's your television that's cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost, a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no tape in the VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:23.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost appeared again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:11:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that is only a trick to give the illusion a ghost is present
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one else had a reason to use this trick that you yourself came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you wanted to say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly like that detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous detective, Sleeping Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:25.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, allow me to explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:34.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth behind the strange phenomena in this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the bloody water in the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever this occurred, there was the strong smell of ammonia in the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was also a weak alcohol scent in the toilet's tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ammonia and alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember, you also did it, during your primary school science classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you take phenolphthalein and alcohol, which are colorless...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And add a few drops of this to the alkaline ammonia...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:09.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It magically turns red as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But can that really work so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this experiment, we get a pinkish-red color.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's different
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:23.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the lighting in this restroom is weak, so we merely think it is blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's the case, you wouldn't get a chemical reaction from urine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Granted, it's true some ammonia is present in urine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Its nature is either neutral or acidic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not an alkaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he needed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This bottle of ammonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you pour it into the bowl's water...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put some phenolphthalein in the tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:53.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A perfect chemical reaction will occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though the ammonia smells bad, no one would think twice about it because the restroom's so dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:12:59.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, boy, where did you find this chemical product?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou asked me to get it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So when everyone else was at the entrance, he had me sneak into a room to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.80,0:13:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a lot of other stuff there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phenolphthalein, chloroform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a scary video tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Scary video tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tape with a scary ghost-like woman saying, "Get out, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:33.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:43.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost my daughter Ran saw on the TV in Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was a movie Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had broadcast from his room with his VCR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you use this apartment's community antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By connecting the output terminal of his VCR to the antenna cable...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sent the video through the antenna...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be received by the television in Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:14.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus broadcasting the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.07,0:14:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To do that, the TV in Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room would have to be on the same channel as the tape...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to begin with, it'd have to be turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Multi-function remote control...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can set it to any TV as long as you know its make and model.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.34,0:14:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using that, you can control any TV in the apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, once I knew the trick, even I could do it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The video that was on my TV before was because of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} cooperated with me in order to broadcast it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the video we took from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:15:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used the remote from the window that faces the building that's under construction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:13.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By standing on the wall, the signal from the remote can reach the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:18.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you can't see it, you can find the right channel based on the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the sun was still shining, you poured chloroform through the gap of the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That caused us to feel weary and fall unconscious in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as one of us awoke in the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With their senses still hazy, you showed them the horrific phantom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's real, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person's shadow that's been peering at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not a person's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you look closely, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:05.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A group of moths, but how!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be precise, an aggregation of male moths.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He sprayed a female moth's pheromone in the shape of a person on the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:22.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, he used black paper to make a mouth and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Male moths were attracted to the scent and gathered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Creating the illusion of someone peering through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof, recall how moths kept landing on my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the shadow appeared for the first time, I nearly fell out of the window on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I instinctively grabbed onto the screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And got some of the pheromone on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.44,0:16:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I removed the screen from the second floor window and put it on this window.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:17:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the person's shadow could disappear on command...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of a black light that would shine from his room, that Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had set up and put on a timer beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moths are even more strongly attracted to UV light, like those from black lights, than they are to pheromones.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if even a single moth remained, the trick would be quickly exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why, when the moths started to dissipate, Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} slammed open the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which caused the remaining moths to be scared away by the shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the fact that you didn't react to the moths when you opened the windowâ€”Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This proves you're the one responsible for the appearances of the ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly, the chemicals are easy to procure, except for the chloroform...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:17:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the scary video tape could have been made by Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with his dolls and a falsetto voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you go through all the trouble to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to make Otonashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} move away by scaring those of us he brought here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:24.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To hide his crime from four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the girl who was killed in the park?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told us that you saw will-o'-the-wisps in the under construction building next door, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a will-o'-the-wisp, but rather the drifting red light from a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:52.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the pale blue light was the light from a portable TV being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone living in that building!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking advantage of that abandoned and still under construction building...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been hiding there this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who was seen by the witness four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit with a large scar on his cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Banchou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is very likely the culprit whose face wasn't seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When someone noticed the cigarette light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His accomplice's hiding place was compromised, prompting him to conceive the ghost story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The goal was to make all the people who lived on the second floor move away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he had been caught, he would have named his accomplice from four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you would have gone to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You moved in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since due to his scar, he couldn't go out in public, so you took him food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:20:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've planned to escape when things had calmed down, but now it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can hear it, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound of your defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sirens from the patrol car I called for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:19.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or I'll curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you aren't a real ghost, you aren't scary at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A backhand...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police arrived and arrested the orchestra-tor of this haunted house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As well as the one hiding in the abandoned building.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ghost story ended the case that occurred four years before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The case from four years ago was due to a huge amount of money being owed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But contrary to the ghost story, this event truly happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the ghost was just a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:22:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I'm not afraid of ghosts anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way that they exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.11,0:23:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.49,0:23:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you tell me something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't express my real nature!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.67,0:23:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Ran's fear of ghosts is one of her charming points.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame for her to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:40.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just get over that personality of yours first
